<add><ab facs="#facs_360_line_1577279753257_3169"><expan>furſt<ex>enlichen</ex></expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add> <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_360_r1l10"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> darynne ewr gnedıge hılff vnd <expan>füdr<ex>ung</ex></expan> <expan>beweiſe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_360_r1l12">wöllet 
<add><ab facs="#facs_360_r1l11">vmb <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add> daʒ Jm dieſelb ſein habe wıder vverde Als etc das </ab>
