<ab><expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>, bysschoff czu Meincz etc.</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns hat <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan>
                        Hanns Dürre, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>, wie im etwievil habe und kauffmanschaft
                                <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> sey worden, der einteil gen
                                <expan>Newe<ex>n</ex>bebemburg</expan>
<expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> sey, darümb er vormals bey
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add>gewesen</add> sey und auch <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> czu
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add><expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan></add>
<expan>ze kume<ex>n</ex></expan> maint, das czu erczelen.
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir von
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add><expan>furst<ex>enlichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan></add>
<expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> darynne ewr gnedige hilff und
                                <expan>füdr<ex>ung</ex></expan>
<expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet <add>umb
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan></add>, daz im dieselb sein habe wider
                        werde. Als etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
